Well my mother - I think she did the best she could - she didn't have much money, you know, they didn't have in those days. And - there wasn't much - going with children, there was only service and - one or two shops yo
u know. There was only mines of-the - for the men. 'Course there was Shildon shops but of course my father never fancied anything down there. The railway - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2627725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 What did your parents think of swearing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6698285 LB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 Well my father never swore in the house. We
 never heard him. But I suppose he could swear down the pit - well I think - you know, so I suppose.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2627725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 When grown ups were tal}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12198054\charrsid418095 k}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid209322\charrsid418095 ing were you allowed to join in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6698285 LB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 Oh no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2627725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 You had to wait until you were spoken to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6698285 LB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 Yes, be seen and not heard they used to say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2627725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 If you did something your parents disapproved of what would happen, who did the punishing if you were naughty?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6698285 LB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 My father used to smack us. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2627725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 Just with his hand?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6698285 LB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 Yes. Or used to have to be sent to bed. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2627725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 How often would you be punished?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6698285 LB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 
Well I remember I got a good smack once, and I can't remember what I did but I can remember I got a smack. From my father. And I could see he was sorry afterwards you know.;
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2627725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 Did you feel it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6698285 LB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 I did feel it, yes. It was harder than usual. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2627725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 Did your mother ever have to smack you or send you to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6698285 LB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 Well - she didn't actually smack yes but she would - sort of give us a tap you know, you mustn't do that anymore.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2627725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 Do you remember any particular occasion when you were punished, you remember being punished but you don't know what for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6698285 LB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 No, I - I can't remember what it was for. Probably }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14628233\charrsid418095 fighting}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095  in the yard with - Annie perhaps you know. I - we used to - I used to have a - a bag of butt
ons once, you know, it - we used to save buttons in those days, and it was probably because she took some of my buttons you know, it might have been that. But I - I remember getting smacked.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2627725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 Do you remember how you felt about being punished?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6698285 LB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 Well I felt sorry, I felt hurt, you know, and I think I rather put it on. He hit me, he didn't intend to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2627725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 He hit you on the head?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6698285 LB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2627725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 You made him feel sorry afterwards did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6698285 LB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 I was rather naughty I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2627725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 Would you say that you 
