\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2627725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 Did you work Saturdays and Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6698285 LB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2627725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 Did you have a half day off at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6698285 LB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2627725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 Were you there long enough to have any holidays with pay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6698285 LB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 No. There wasn't any holidays with pay those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2627725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 Did you do any cooking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6698285 LB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 No, I didn't in that house, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2627725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 What were you paid?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6698285 LB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 Half a crown for a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2627725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 Did you feel that was a fair wage or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6698285 LB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 No I didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2627725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 Did you give any of the money to your mother?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6698285 LB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 It all went to mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2627725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 What would she spend it on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6698285 LB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 Well it would go in the kitty I think, you know, it would sort of help out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2627725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 How did you get on with the other people you worked with there?
