\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6698285 LB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 Yes. I was there five years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2627725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 So that would be 'til 1920?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6698285 LB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2627725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 Did you have any holidays with pay there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6698285 LB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 Yes, I used to get a months holiday at - in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Leeds{\*\xmlclose}
, yes, because the - there was Mrs Boyd and her sister lived together, was just the two of them, and - they - they used to have a months holiday. And I got a months holiday with pay.
