\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2627725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 So you used to save it up and give to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6698285 LB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid209322\charrsid418095 Yes.
